## Per-module specs

Detailed specs for each module live under `.claude/specs/<ModuleName>/<ModuleName>Spec_1.md`.

## Adding a new module

Use `/project-init:add-module "<ModuleName> — short description"` to scaffold Core/Infrastructure/Api + Tests, wire the `.slnx` and `appsettings.json`, and create a starting spec.
